#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:19
msgid "Apply Texture"
msgstr "Aplicar Textura"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:21
msgid ""
"The digiKam Apply Texture is a tool for applying decorative textures to an "
"image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:23
msgid ""
"By adding texture to your image, whether color or black and white, you can "
"make it look like an oil painting on canvas, an Old Masters etching, a Pop "
"Art portrait composed of enlarged half-tone dots, or even a mural on a brick "
"wall. The Decorate --> Apply Texture Image Editor menu can be used for that."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:27
msgid "Two options give you control over the texture applying on image:"
msgstr ""
"Existem duas opções que lhe dão o controlo sobre a aplicação de texturas à "
"imagem:"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:29
msgid ""
"Type: this option specifies the decorative texture style to apply under the "
"image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:31
msgid ""
"Relief: dragging this option to the right increases the appearance of depth "
"or three-dimensionality of the texture on image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:34
msgid "Add Border"
msgstr "Adicionar um Contorno"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:36
msgid ""
"The digiKam Add Border is a tool to frame an image with decorative borders."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:38
msgid ""
"Keeping the viewer's interest within the confines of the edges of a "
"photograph is not a simple task. One of the simplest ways to hold the "
"attention on an image is to incorporate a decorative frame around an image. "
"It acts as a kind of psychological barrier to the straying eye. The Image --"
"> Add Border Image Editor menu can be used for that."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:42
msgid "Four options give you control over the decorative frame rendering:"
msgstr ""
"Existem quatro opções que lhe dão o controlo sobre o desenho da moldura "
"decorativa:"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:44
msgid ""
"Type: this option specifies the decorative frame style to apply around the "
"image. Solid style just surrounds the image with a colored line, Niepce "
"style surrounds the image with a fine line and a large border (ideal for "
"black and white images), Beveled style adds a neat dimension to your image "
"(ideal to create a button effect), and Decorative style adds an ornamental "
"border using patterns."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:46
msgid ""
"Width: this option specifies the border width in percents of image size. The "
"border is added around the image. The width range is limited between 1% and "
"50%."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:48
msgid ""
"First: this option specifies the first color to use with the current border "
"type."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:50
msgid ""
"Second: this option specifies the second color to use with the current "
"border type."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:52
msgid "Click on the OK button to apply the border around the current image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:56
msgid ""
"The border decorated target image will be bigger than the original, but it "
"will retain the same aspect ratio. This is important for printing images, "
"especially if you have used the Aspect Ratio Crop tool before."
msgstr ""
"A imagem decorada de destino será maior que o original, mas irá usar à mesma "
"as mesmas proporções de tamanho. Esta forma é importante para imprimir as "
"imagens, especialmente se tiver usado o Recorte Proporcional antes desta "
"ferramenta."

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:59
msgid "Insert Text"
msgstr "Inserir um Texto"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:61
msgid "The digiKam Insert Text is a tool for adding text to an image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:63
msgid ""
"This is a handy tool as it lets you add formatted text easily to an image "
"wherever you want, at several places when needed."
msgstr ""
"Esta é uma ferramenta útil na medida em que lhe permite adicionar texto "
"formatado facilmente numa imagem, sempre que o desejar, em vários locais se "
"necessário."

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:67
msgid ""
"This tool seems very intuitive to use. Type in your text and place it with "
"the mouse. Use the block settings as you please. Choose the orientation, "
"color from a color space, and fonts with all their properties. You will have "
"to scale the font size to the image size, the larger the image, the larger "
"the font has to be! Finally choose to add a border around the text and/or a "
"semitransparent background. Voilà, it's finished!"
msgstr ""
"Esta ferramenta parece ser muito intuitiva de usar. Escreva o seu texto e "
"coloque-o com o rato. Use a configuração do bloco como desejar. Escolha a "
"orientação, a cor a partir de um espaço de cores e os tipos de letra com "
"todas as suas propriedades. Terá de definir a escala to tamanho de letra "
"como sendo o tamanho da imagem, sendo que quanto maior a imagem, maior terá "
"de ser o tipo de letra! Finalmente, opte por adicionar um contorno em torno "
"do texto e/ou um fundo semi-transparente. É tudo!"

#: ../../image_editor/decorate_tools.rst:69
msgid ""
"Any text setting you have chosen can always be changed as long as you don't "
"click the OK button. In saved and reloaded images the text has become part "
"of the image, it cannot be changed anymore."
msgstr ""
"Todas as configurações de texto que tenha escolhido poderão sempre ser "
"alteradas, desde que não carregue no botão OK. Nas imagens gravadas e "
"carregadas de novo, o texto tornou-se parte da imagem, pelo que não poderá "
"ser mais alterado."
